---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Asset Management — Onchain Yield">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">資產管理</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">How Funds Access Onchain Yield</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">基金如何獲取鏈上收益</span>
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">In February 2026, BlackRock's BUIDL — a tokenized US Treasury fund — was listed on Uniswap, the largest decentralized exchange. Each BUIDL token represents a share in a fund holding short-term US government securities, with yield accruing daily. The fund has grown from $200 million at launch to roughly $2.4 billion in under two years, and is now available on nine blockchains including Ethereum, Solana, and Avalanche.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">2026年2月，BlackRock的BUIDL — 一隻代幣化美國國債基金 — 在最大的去中心化交易所Uniswap上市。每個BUIDL代幣代表持有短期美國政府證券基金的一個份額，收益每日累計。該基金在推出後不到兩年內從$2億增長至約$24億，目前可在包括Ethereum、Solana和Avalanche在內的9條區塊鏈上使用。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">This is not a crypto-native experiment. BlackRock manages $11.5 trillion. Franklin Templeton, which manages $1.5 trillion, has its own tokenized government money fund — BENJI (ticker: FOBXX) — with $742 million in assets, operating on Stellar and Polygon. Ondo Finance, backed by BlackRock, Fidelity, and Wellington Management, has $2.75 billion in total value locked across its tokenized treasury products. The total market for tokenized US Treasuries now exceeds $10 billion.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">這不是crypto原生實驗。BlackRock管理$11.5萬億資產。Franklin Templeton管理$1.5萬億資產，其代幣化政府貨幣市場基金BENJI（代碼：FOBXX）持有$7.42億資產，在Stellar和Polygon上運營。由BlackRock、Fidelity和Wellington Management支持的Ondo Finance，其代幣化美債產品的總鎖定價值達$27.5億。代幣化美國國債的總市場規模現已超過$100億。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">For fund managers, the relevant question is not "should we look at crypto?" — it's "do we want our Treasury allocation earning the same yield but with 24/7 liquidity, real-time NAV, and the ability to use it as collateral across multiple protocols simultaneously?"</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">對基金經理而言，相關問題不是「我們是否應該關注加密？」— 而是「我們是否希望國債配置獲得相同收益，但擁有24/7流動性、實時資產淨值，以及同時在多個協議中用作抵押品的能力？」</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Why Put Treasuries Onchain</span><span class="lang-zh">為什麼將美債上鏈</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Three structural advantages explain why $10 billion has moved onchain in under three years.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">三個結構性優勢解釋了為何$100億在不到三年內轉移到鏈上。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Composability.</span> Tokenized treasuries can serve as collateral across DeFi lending protocols, margin accounts, and structured products — simultaneously. One asset, multiple uses. Binance already accepts BUIDL as trading collateral. Morpho, an onchain lending protocol, has over $620 million in RWA (real-world asset) deposits functioning as an onchain prime brokerage layer. Your Treasury allocation can earn yield while simultaneously serving as collateral for other positions.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">可組合性。</span>代幣化美債可同時在DeFi借貸協議、保證金賬戶和結構化產品中用作抵押品。一種資產，多重用途。Binance已接受BUIDL作為交易抵押品。鏈上借貸協議Morpho持有超過$6.2億的RWA（現實世界資產）存款，充當鏈上主經紀商角色。你的國債配置可以在賺取收益的同時用作其他倉位的抵押品。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">24/7 access.</span> No custody transfer delays. No settlement windows. Subscriptions and redemptions happen in minutes, not days. WisdomTree received SEC approval in February 2026 for 24/7 trading of its tokenized money market fund at a fixed $1 intraday price — the first of its kind. Asian investors don't need to wait for US market hours.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">24/7准入。</span>無託管轉移延遲。無結算窗口。認購和贖回在數分鐘內完成，而非數天。WisdomTree於2026年2月獲SEC批准，以固定$1日內價格24/7交易其代幣化貨幣市場基金 — 這是同類首創。亞洲投資者無需等待美國市場時段。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Transparency.</span> Holdings are verifiable onchain. NAV is real-time, not end-of-day. The audit trail is immutable. This is a higher standard of transparency than traditional fund structures, and it costs less to maintain.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">透明度。</span>持倉可在鏈上驗證。資產淨值實時更新，而非日終。審計記錄不可篡改。這是比傳統基金結構更高的透明度標準，且維護成本更低。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Yield Spectrum: From Conservative to Growth</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">收益光譜：從保守到增長</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The safest entry point is the one most familiar: tokenized Treasuries. BUIDL and BENJI are backed by the same short-term US government securities as any money market fund, yielding roughly 4.5% annualized. The additional risk is limited to smart contract exposure — the code that holds and distributes the tokens. For funds with a fiduciary obligation, BlackRock and Franklin Templeton are familiar, auditable counterparties.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">最安全的切入點是最熟悉的：代幣化美債。BUIDL和BENJI由與任何貨幣市場基金相同的短期美國政府證券支持，年化收益約4.5%。額外風險僅限於智能合約敞口 — 即持有和分發代幣的代碼。對於有受託義務的基金，BlackRock和Franklin Templeton是熟悉的、可審計的交易對手。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">One step further: stablecoin lending. Supplying USDC to institutional-grade lending protocols like Aave (which holds 56.5% of total DeFi debt) or Morpho generates 3 to 8% APR depending on market conditions. The risk profile adds smart contract exposure and borrower liquidation risk, mitigated by over-collateralization — borrowers must post more collateral than they borrow.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">更進一步：穩定幣借貸。向機構級借貸協議如Aave（佔DeFi總債務的56.5%）或Morpho提供USDC可產生3至8%年化收益，視市場狀況而定。風險概況增加了智能合約敞口和借款人清算風險，通過超額抵押緩解 — 借款人必須提供超過借款額的抵押品。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">For funds comfortable with more active strategies, ETH staking yields roughly 3 to 4% APR for participating in Ethereum's proof-of-stake consensus — and the SFC approved staking for licensed VATPs in Hong Kong in April 2025, making this a regulated yield product. Liquid staking tokens (stETH, rETH) allow continued use of capital while staking. Yield-bearing stablecoins grew from $9.5 billion to over $20 billion during 2025, averaging around 5% yield.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">對於接受更主動策略的基金，ETH質押通過參與Ethereum權益證明共識可獲得約3至4%年化收益 — 而SFC已於2025年4月批准香港持牌VATP提供質押服務，使其成為受監管的收益產品。流動質押代幣（stETH、rETH）允許在質押同時繼續使用資金。收益型穩定幣在2025年從$95億增長至超過$200億，平均收益約5%。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Hong Kong Enablers</span><span class="lang-zh">香港的推動因素</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong's regulatory environment increasingly supports institutional onchain yield. Twelve licensed VATPs provide regulated on/off ramps for institutional capital. The SFC's staking approval means regulated crypto yield is now real — not theoretical. The family office tax concession, effective February 2026, treats digital asset profits the same as equities and bonds. And the banking layer is ready: Standard Chartered offers spot crypto trading, HSBC runs tokenized deposits via Orion, and both are among applicants for stablecoin issuer licenses.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">香港的監管環境越來越支持機構級鏈上收益。12間持牌VATP為機構資金提供受監管的出入金通道。SFC的質押批准意味著受監管的加密收益已成現實 — 而非理論。2026年2月生效的家族辦公室稅務優惠將數字資產利潤與股票和債券同等對待。銀行基礎設施已就緒：渣打提供現貨加密交易，HSBC通過Orion運營代幣化存款，兩者都是穩定幣發行牌照的申請人。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The infrastructure for institutional onchain yield in Hong Kong is not coming — it's here. The remaining question is allocation sizing and mandate structuring, not whether the plumbing exists.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">香港機構級鏈上收益的基礎設施不是即將到來 — 它已經在這裡了。剩下的問題是配置規模和授權結構，而非管道是否存在。</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Exploring onchain yield for your fund?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">為你的基金探索鏈上收益？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We can walk through the options and risk profiles relevant to your mandate.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們可以詳細討論與你的投資授權相關的選項和風險概況。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
